    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> domno
                        bone recordationis <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs> Aderici <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> nostri, tibi <persName key="#Prevosts"
                            ref="#people/113">Crissio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> quod
                        constructum esse videtur infra hanc nostram Beneventanam civitatem, integram
                        modicam <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Landed_possessions">terricellam</rs> cum integra <rs
                                key="#Wine">vineola</rs></rs> que fuit <name ref="Alahis"
                            >Alahis</name>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi hominis</rs>, in loco qui Fabrica vocatur,
                            <placeName ref="#places/3464"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">finibus
                            Folianense</placeName>, veluti legibus <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >ad sacrum nostrum evenit palatium pro quo sine heredes decessit</rs>,
                        in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum
                        preceptum supra dicta integra terricella et vineolam tu et posteris tui
                        habere et possidere valeatis et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary" ref="#people/3466">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventum</placeName> primo anno, mense iunio, quarta
                        decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
